---
import EditorialPage from "../layouts/EditorialPage.astro";

const seo = {
  title: "The Longer Version — Haris Samingan",
  description: "The values, daily life, and hard decisions shaping Haris Samingan.",
  image: "/haris.jpg",
};
---

<EditorialPage
  seo={seo}
  eyebrow="Beyond the short bio"
  title="The longer version"
  intro="Life is too short not to share, in my opinion. What’s the worst that can happen?"
>
  <section class="transparency-section">
    <h2>Value #1 — Transparency</h2>
    <div class="truths">
      <p>
        <strong class="truth-label">Sexuality:</strong>
        <span
          class="identity-reveal"
          tabindex="0"
          aria-label="I don’t fancy girls. I’m gay."
        >
          <span>I don’t fancy girls.</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">I’m gay.</span>
        </span>
      </p>
      <p>
        I’m Malay, but I’m not Muslim. I have renounced my religion.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Hard conversations and decisions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li data-index="01">
        <strong>With my mum.</strong>
        I told her that I forgive her for not treating my late grandma well.
      </li>
      <li data-index="02">
        <strong>With my little brother.</strong>
        I told him directly about habits I don’t like, including gaslighting.
      </li>
      <li data-index="03">
        <strong>With my big brother.</strong>
        I blocked his phone number after he asked me for money. I still hang out
        with him; I just don’t want to be his piggy bank.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="happier-now">
      There have been many more hard conversations and difficult decisions. I’m
      much happier now.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>My day to day</h2>
    <ol class="daily-routine">
      <li data-index="5:00 AM"><strong>Wake up.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="5:30 AM"><strong>Run or exercise.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="7:00 AM"><strong>Nap.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="9:00 AM"><strong>Work.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="12:00 PM"><strong>Lunch.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="1:00 PM"><strong>Nap again.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="2:00 PM"><strong>Work again.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="6:00 PM"><strong>Exercise.</strong></li>
      <li data-index="10:00 PM">
        <strong>Sleep.</strong>
        I usually sleep in just my underwear.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Moving out</h2>
    <p>
      I moved out of my parents’ house mainly because I need 100% focus to
      achieve what I want to do. Having my own space gives me the independence,
      quiet, and control over my routine that I need.
    </p>
  </section>
</EditorialPage>

<style>
  .transparency-section > h2 {
    margin-bottom: 22px !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    border-bottom: 0 !important;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 10vw, 58px) !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em !important;
    line-height: 0.98 !important;
    text-transform: none !important;
    color: var(--ink) !important;
  }

  .truths {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .truths p {
    margin: 0 !important;
    padding: 17px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .identity-reveal {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-grid;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.62;
    cursor: help;
    outline: none;
  }

  .truth-label {
    display: inline;
    margin-right: 5px;
    color: var(--quiet);
    font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 650;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    vertical-align: 4px;
  }

  .identity-reveal span {
    grid-area: 1 / 1;
    transition: opacity 180ms ease, transform 180ms ease;
  }

  .identity-reveal span:last-child {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(5px);
  }

  .identity-reveal:hover span:first-child,
  .identity-reveal:focus-visible span:first-child {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .identity-reveal:hover span:last-child,
  .identity-reveal:focus-visible span:last-child {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .identity-reveal:focus-visible {
    box-shadow: 0 2px 0 var(--accent);
  }

  .happier-now {
    margin-top: 22px !important;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 25px !important;
    line-height: 1.25 !important;
    color: var(--ink) !important;
  }

  .daily-routine li {
    min-height: 52px;
    padding-left: 98px;
  }

  .daily-routine li::before {
    width: 72px;
    font-style: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .identity-reveal span {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
